      <title>Got Flat Feet?</title>
      <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/HomeExerciseEquipmentReviewsAndTips/~3/Bij8mdqXJLs/got-flat-feet.html</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Apr 2012 17:52:20 GMT</pubDate>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[Are your feet flat? Do you suffer from shin splints? Well, step right up sir or ma'am to the greatest cure-all since ....<br />
