<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
<a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-8zAkwKR0sH8/T5GdPi8fsKI/AAAAAAAABj4/MlNG2WuO0os/s1600/asics+womens+gel+evolution+6.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="200" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-8zAkwKR0sH8/T5GdPi8fsKI/AAAAAAAABj4/MlNG2WuO0os/s200/asics+womens+gel+evolution+6.jpg" width="200" /></a></div>
Actually, we have found some shoes that might help you. At least that's what we glean from the men and women that have tried them and gotten relief from their particular foot aches and pains. <br />
<br />
We are talking about the Asics Gel Evolution 6 shoes for men and women. Let's take a look at what some happy users of these shoes have to say.<br />
<br />
First, take the case of<i> Azazello</i> who runs approximately 20 miles or so a week. He does this even with "extremely flat feet and overpronation." Azazello says his new Gel Evolution 6 running shoes have good support and are "really comfortable".<br />
<br />
Jon reported running with no pain after the initial breaking in phase.<br />
<br />
<blockquote class="tr_bq">
<i>"I have flat foot, and i was also a little overweight, which lead to shin splints that makes running almost impossible for me.<br />I've
 decided to buy these shoes and give it a try. In the first 2 weeks I 
ran and played tennis with them. But the pain was still there. After 2 
weeks pain started to reduce, I started to run better, changed my eating
 style to a more healthy one. And now I've been running with them for 
almost 6 months now, and I have no pain,  I'm healthier, more fit and I 
can run better. These shoes worked magical for me, not only lead me to a
 painless run, but inspired me to loose weight.<br /><br />I strongly 
recommend them if you suffer from shin splints. They don't look very 
nice (but beauty is in the eye of beholder) so you can't wear them under
 jeans really, but they function so well that I'm giving it 5 stars.<br /><br />Also i received the shipping quickly and without problems from Amazon"</i> </blockquote>
<a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B003OYJ0KA/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B003OYJ0KA">Get the Best Deals on ASICS Men's GEL-Evolution 6 Running Shoes here.</a><img alt="" border="0" height="1" src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=folthenewyory-20&amp;l=as2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B003OYJ0KA" style="border: none !important; margin: 0px !important;" width="1" /><br />
<br />
Ladies love Gel Foundation 6 shoes as well. <i>Modchic</i> tells us that she is "flat-footed, over-weight, and I over-pronate..." . She even has pain when going barefoot. With the help of this "great shoe", Mod is looking forward to walking and eventually even running again.<br />
<br />
<i>S.King</i>, who calls her Gel Foundation 6s "the best running shoes yet", offers some advice.<br />
<br />
<blockquote class="tr_bq">
<i>" ... I tried on several running shoes in sneaker stores.  The salespeople 
always try to sell me the Asics Kayanos (the most expensive Asics...but I
 feel uncomfortable the second I put Kayanos on) and stores don't all 
stock the Asics Evolution so I ordered it from amazon hoping I would 
love this model as I have loved my previous generations of the Asics 
Evolution.  Its the best so far!  The comfort of slippers and every part
 of my foot feels properly supported as opposed to other sneakers that 
feel like my foot only touches certain areas or overcorrects.  I had 
chronic ankle soreness that I was learning to live with that disappeared
 within days of using my new evolutions."</i></blockquote>
&nbsp;<a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B003OYJ1CW/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B003OYJ1CW">Learn more or Buy the ASICS Women's GEL-Evolution 6 Running Shoes here.</a><br />
<br />
We found 26 customer reviews for the women's Asics Gel Evolution 6. The combined score was an outstanding 4.4 out of a possible 5.0 grade. The men's Gel Evolution 6 received a 4.0 out of 5.0 stars.<br />
<br />
&nbsp;If you suffer from flat feet and tend to over-pronate, these may be the shoes for you.<br />
