    <item>
      <title>Can Anyone Tell Me Which Are The Best Walking Shoes?</title>
      <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/HomeExerciseEquipmentReviewsAndTips/~3/VwwmdOWnU9I/can-anyone-tell-me-which-are-best.html</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Apr 2012 13:38:56 GMT</pubDate>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[With all the walking shoes on the market today, it is very easy to become confused with information overload. No wonder a reader asks, "Which brand is best for walking?"<br />
<br />
<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
<a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-V7hbMyVn3yI/T5E8q22vzpI/AAAAAAAABjw/vQWsmJI-xJw/s1600/Walking-Shoes-in-Motion.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="200" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-V7hbMyVn3yI/T5E8q22vzpI/AAAAAAAABjw/vQWsmJI-xJw/s200/Walking-Shoes-in-Motion.jpg" width="200" /></a></div>
While recognizing that there are all kinds of feet and walking situations, we recommend you check out the walking line from New Balance. ( This is from someone that walks a hour everyday. ) I've bought pair after pair of New Balance shoes for everyday life - walking, standing, shopping, etc.<br />
<br />
If your feet have special conditions such as plantar fasciitis or if you need a special shoe because of diabetes, check out <a href="http://www.amazon.com/mn/search/?_encoding=UTF8&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;field-keywords=new%20balance%20927&amp;url=search-alias%3Daps" target="_blank">New Balance 927 walking shoes</a><img alt="" border="0" height="1" src="https://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=folthenewyory-20&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=1" style="border: none !important; margin: 0px !important;" width="1" />.<br />
<br />
They have features like a seamless&nbsp; inner liner that reduces irritation to your feet.<br />
 <br />
<br />
<a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B003VWBO4K/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B003VWBO4K">AVIA Men's A339M Walking Shoes</a><img alt="" border="0" height="1" src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=folthenewyory-20&amp;l=as2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B003VWBO4K" style="border: none !important; margin: 0px !important;" width="1" /> are good economical walking shoes. When we checked, they were less than $50. Customers seem to be pleased with these shoes Here is what one reviewer (&nbsp; <i>Dingle98</i> ) wrote.<br />
<br />
<blockquote class="tr_bq">
<i>"Having been unhappy with most of my choices of walking shoes over the 
last few decades...despite paying more and more over time, I decided 
this time I'd check reviews on Amazon...and this particular Avia shoe 
had an extraordinary percentage of very satisfied buyers.<br /><br />Add my 
endorsement to them. This is by far the most comfortable walking shoe 
I've ever had. Fits like a glove, comfortable to use for extended 
periods, and the price was excellent.<br /><br />Did take the advice of a couple of previous buyers and ordered a size larger than normal and that worked out perfect"</i></blockquote>
<br />
<a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0039237FG/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B0039237FG">ASICS Women's GEL-Resort 2 Walking Shoes</a><img alt="" border="0" height="1" src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=folthenewyory-20&amp;l=as2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B0039237FG" style="border: none !important; margin: 0px !important;" width="1" /> feature the famous Asics Gel Cushioning system that attenuates shock. Women were generally happy with their purchase of these shoes. This review from <i>S. Lewis</i> is typical.<br />
<br />
<blockquote class="tr_bq">
<i>"I needed some new walking shoes that would support my feet well and this
 brand was recommended to me. I was surprised by the reasonable price. 
They are great! Very comfortable and, so far, after 2 months are holding
 up well. My only regret is that I couldn't get the pink stripe instead 
of the blue... But, I wasn't going to pay $20 more just to have pink. 
Great shoes, highly recommend!"
