      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Apr 2012 18:24:36 GMT</pubDate>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<br />
<div class="separator" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: center;">
<a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0058C6N6K/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B0058C6N6K" target="_blank"><img border="0" height="139" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-hBkRonfhEVo/T4cK9c4xahI/AAAAAAAABis/Va0JVzMaBK4/s320/asics+gt+2170.jpg" width="320" /></a></div>
<br />
Asics GT 2170 Men's running shoes are the latest updating of Asics most popular shoes. Why are these shoes so popular? Let's see what the men who wear them have to say.<br />
<br />
<i>Gary</i> calls his GT 2170 s&nbsp; the "best running shoes ever!". Why is Gary so enthusiastic? <br />
<br />
 <br />
<div style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;">
<span style="font-size: small;"><br /></span></div>
<div style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;">
<span style="font-size: small;">We found the best deals for the Asics GT 2170 running shoes, and many other running shoes, at Amazon. <b><a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0058C6N6K/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B0058C6N6K">Buy your ASICS Men's Gt-2170 Running Shoes from Amazon and save.</a><img alt="" border="0" height="1" src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=folthenewyory-20&amp;l=as2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B0058C6N6K" style="border: medium none ! important; margin: 0px ! important;" width="1" />
&nbsp; </b></span></div>
<br />
&nbsp;A combination of "...Plantar Fasciitis in both feet and a painful heel spur in the right" along with a lot of running was causing him to be uncomfortable in his shoes after using them for just a few miles.<br />
<br />
He tried Brooks, Saucony, Nike, New Balance shoes and even a few Asics models without getting satisfaction. Finally, Gary tried a pair of Asics Gt 2170 running shoes. ( I think you know where this is going.) Here is how Gary put it.<br />
<br />
<blockquote class="tr_bq">
<i>" ... Without any doubt, I can honestly tell you that I now have my best pair 
of running shoes I've ever owned. There is plenty of gel, foam, cushion 
and yet a firm-like support structure throughout the shoes that I can't 
recall ever feeling and now makes me want to run further than before and
 has got me feeling the joy of running when I first started to get into 
the sport. Even the sides of my feet are feeling good after a 10 mile 
run this morning. ..."</i></blockquote>
<i>Oswald </i>is not a runner but says his Asics Gt 2170s are <i>"terrific for walking and daily wear."</i> He especially likes their light weight and great arch support. When the time comes to buy a new pair of shoes, Oswald says he'll be shopping for Asics Gel shoes.<br />
<br />
On the other hand, <i>pep</i> was not impressed. He owned a pair of Brooks GTS Adrenaline 11s and found the transition from heel to toe<i> " ... no where near a smooth as the Brooks. ..."</i>&nbsp; But his was the only negative review we saw.<br />
<br />
Bill described himself as an <i>"out of shape guy who wanted to get back into shape and running"</i>.<span style="vertical-align: middle;"> For the price range, Bill thought his Gt 2170s were definitely the most comfortable shoes out there. He loved the look, feel, and value. He says,<i> "Get these shoes, you wont be disappointed!" </i><b><a href="http://www.amazon.com/review/B0058C6N6K/?_encoding=UTF8&amp;showViewpoints=1&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957" target="_blank">Read the latest customer reviews of the Asics GT 2170 running shoes here.</a></b></span><br />
<br />
<br />
