I workout in an empty corner of my office. Others report being able to comfortably get in their P90X workouts from a hotel room, den, or bedroom. A 6 foot by 9 foot area next to a television with a DVD player and a door frame are all you need and you're ready to "Bring It" and get into the best shape of your life.<br />
