    <item>
      <title>Dumbbells for Women</title>
      <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/HomeExerciseEquipmentReviewsAndTips/~3/oDjIgfJcf5Q/dumbbells-for-women.html</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Mar 2012 16:44:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-pof6zHlT_5M/T1eqrXnCVvI/AAAAAAAABgU/7SWdeYWkdW0/s1600/bowflex-selecttech-552-woman.jpg"><img style="float:left; margin:0 10px 10px 0;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 300px; height: 300px;" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-pof6zHlT_5M/T1eqrXnCVvI/AAAAAAAABgU/7SWdeYWkdW0/s400/bowflex-selecttech-552-woman.jpg" alt="" id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5717225914018977522" border="0" /></a>When it comes to fitness, the needs and preferences of women are often different that those of men. Dumbbells for women must match the particular needs of women.<br /><br />While recognizing that each woman is an individual, most women do not want to develop large, bulky muscles when they exercise.<br /><br />This causes many to avoid weights altogether. But the proper set of dumbbells combined with the right fitness plan can deliver the lean, toned look that many women desire.<br /><br />Below we will highlight some of the more popular dumbbell sets that women are using, enjoying, and gaining health benefits from.<br /><br /><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-KUkJQcufv48/T1ev727XTbI/AAAAAAAABgg/Hb9nz8vZbu4/s1600/Altus%2BAthletic%2B32-Pound%2BDumbbell%2BSet.jpg"><img style="float:right; margin:0 0 10px 10px;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 200px; height: 200px;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-KUkJQcufv48/T1ev727XTbI/AAAAAAAABgg/Hb9nz8vZbu4/s200/Altus%2BAthletic%2B32-Pound%2BDumbbell%2BSet.jpg" alt="" id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5717231694861782450" border="0" /></a>The <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0032HONJW/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B0032HONJW">Altus Athletic 32-Pound Dumbbell Set</a><img src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=folthenewyory-20&amp;l=as2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B0032HONJW" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;" border="0" height="1" width="1" /> comes with a stand to organize and store your dumbbell sets. The set includes pairs of 3 pound, 5 pound, and 8 pound weight - perfect for the fitness needs of many women. The steel dumbbells are covered with soft neoprene for comfort.<br /><br />This dumbbell set for women received a 4.8 out of 5 star rating from the combined scores of 16 customer reviews at Amazon. Here is how one review put it. <span style="font-style: italic;">"I bought this for my daughter who is 16 and she loves it. She wants to  work out with different weights not too heavy so she can keep herself in  shape. It made me too want to exercise. "</span><br /><br />( 214 )<br /><br /><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-CmDCv0p-TEo/T1eyVWaFBbI/AAAAAAAABgs/jlRoEWte90w/s1600/tone%2Bfitness.jpg"><img style="float:right; margin:0 0 10px 10px;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 200px; height: 200px;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-CmDCv0p-TEo/T1eyVWaFBbI/AAAAAAAABgs/jlRoEWte90w/s200/tone%2Bfitness.jpg" alt="" id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5717234331832092082" border="0" /></a>A similar dumbbell set is offered by Tone Fitness. Their <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B003P90K58/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B003P90K58"> 20-Pound Hourglass Shaped Dumbbell Set</a><img src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=folthenewyory-20&amp;l=as2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B003P90K58" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;" border="0" height="1" width="1" /> includes a storage rack. It has pairs of 2, 3, and 5 pound dumbbells.<br /><br />The hourglass shape is not only stylish, it also is easy to handle. A neoprene coating makes the weights softer and more comfortable.<br /><br />Twenty-one customer reviews gave this dumbbell set a combined score of 4.3 out of a possible 5 stars.<br /><br />Most reviewers were happy with their purchase but a few thought the storage rack was rather cheaply made. Here is what one happy customer wrote.<br /><br /><span style="font-style: italic;"></span><blockquote><span style="font-style: italic;">" I bought these dumbbell a few weeks ago and I have been very happy with  the quality. I use them for walking and some light toning exercises.  They have a nice grip and the weight sizes are perfect for me. I love  the fun colors too. The set comes with a plastic rack that holds the  dumbbells together nicely and keeps them off the floor. I will be buying  some more sets to give away for X-mas!       "</span></blockquote><br /><br /><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-0itHtnr6h6Q/T1ezzWZzwjI/AAAAAAAABg4/ZfiZcSS44Tk/s1600/jillian%2Bmichaels%2Bdumbbells.jpg"><img style="float:right; margin:0 0 10px 10px;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 200px; height: 200px;" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-0itHtnr6h6Q/T1ezzWZzwjI/AAAAAAAABg4/ZfiZcSS44Tk/s200/jillian%2Bmichaels%2Bdumbbells.jpg" alt="" id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5717235946738663986" border="0" /></a>Jillian Michaels offers an adjustable set of dumbbells. The aptly named <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0045GRJCM/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B0045GRJCM">Jillian Michaels Ultimate 12.5  Adjustable Speed Dumbbells</a><img src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=folthenewyory-20&amp;l=as2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B0045GRJCM" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;" border="0" height="1" width="1" /> lets you quickly adjust each dumbbell from 2.5 lbs to 12.5 lbs.<br /><br />This system lets you have the advantages of eight different sets of dumbbells without the storage and clutter concerns. While the weight plates are made of cast iron the handle grips are soft. An exercise chart is included with your purchase.<br /><br /><br />*****<br /><br />See also: <a href="http://www.squidoo.com/dumbbell-weights-for-women">Dumbbell Weights for Women</a><div class="blogger-post-footer"><img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/4492444098437691579-3239046734278332060?l=home-exercise-equipment.blogspot.com' alt='' /></div>
<p><a href="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/dwjsUTFl4M_-rJsdwIo8-YhoXXs/0/da"><img src="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/dwjsUTFl4M_-rJsdwIo8-YhoXXs/0/di" border="0" ismap="true"></img></a><br/>
<a href="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/dwjsUTFl4M_-rJsdwIo8-YhoXXs/1/da"><img src="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/dwjsUTFl4M_-rJsdwIo8-YhoXXs/1/di" border="0" ismap="true"></img></a></p><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/HomeExerciseEquipmentReviewsAndTips/~4/oDjIgfJcf5Q" height="1" width="1"/>]]></content:encoded>
      <enclosure url="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/home-exercise-equipment-reviews-and-tips/Home_Exercise_Equipment_Reviews_And_Tips-Dumbbells_for_Women.mp3" length="1479534" type="audio/mpeg" />
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Proform Treadmill 400 Review</title>
      <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/HomeExerciseEquipmentReviewsAndTips/~3/pAPB2ByGhO8/proform-treadmill-400-review.html</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Mar 2012 17:07:42 GMT</pubDate>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-NkZjdExC1Kg/T1DwqWe2afI/AAAAAAAABgI/HhDNPBviIxk/s1600/proform%2Btreadmill%2B400.jpg"><img style="float:left; margin:0 10px 10px 0;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 311px; height: 276px;" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-NkZjdExC1Kg/T1DwqWe2afI/AAAAAAAABgI/HhDNPBviIxk/s400/proform%2Btreadmill%2B400.jpg" alt="" id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5715332537513306610" border="0" /></a><br />The <span style="font-weight: bold;">Proform Treadmill 400</span> is packed with features that will make your treadmill workouts more enjoyable and more productive.<br /><br />This is a performance treadmill that will challenge you with so much variety that you'll never have to worry about a boring treadmill workout again.<br /><br />With features like the <span style="font-style: italic;">ProTech™ Cushioning</span> shock absorption system to protect your joints and the <span style="font-style: italic;">Dual-Grip EKG™ Heart Rate Monitor</span>          to help keep you safely within your target heart rate, the Proform Treadmill 400 is a home treadmill made with your well being in mind.<br /><br />Perhaps the most exciting feature of this treadmill from Proform is the <span style="font-weight: bold;">iFit® Workout Card Technology</span>. The Lose Weight iFit Workout Card is designed by Jillian Michaels. It includes 24 progressive workouts that are organized into 8 week fat burning sessions.<br /><br /><a href="http://www.anrdoezrs.net/click-3489386-10460334?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.proform.com%2Fwebapp%2Fwcs%2Fstores%2Fservlet%2FProduct_-1_14201_16002_64001_157411&amp;cjsku=PFTL49610" target="_top"><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">Get more information or buy the ProForm 400 CT Treadmill now.</span></a><img style="font-weight: bold;" src="http://www.awltovhc.com/image-3489386-10460334" border="0" height="1" width="1" /><br /><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">Here are some more features of the Proform Treadmill 400.</span><br /><ul><li>It is a folding treadmill. Why not free up some space while the treadmill is not in use? The running deck folds up.<br /></li><li>A large viewing angle on the ClearView™ Display makes the readouts clear and easy to ready whether you are tall or short. From the console you can track your speed, time, distance, incline, pulse and calories burned.</li><li>The warranties offered by Proform are generous. The ProForm 400 CT is protected with a Lifetime Frame Warranty, 25-Year Motor Warranty and 90 Days Parts &amp; Labor.          </li><li>The music port is compatible with your iPod or MP3 device. </li><li>The 2.25 CHP Mach Z™ Motor is powerful and quiet. The self cooling drive system quiets noise while cooling the internal components.</li><li>The treadbelt is 20 inches wide and 55 inches long. This is enough room for most people when running on a treadmill.<br /></li><li>Quick™ Speed controls let you change speeds in an instant just with the touch of a button. The speed range is from 0 to 10 miles per hour.</li><li>The 0-10% Quick™ Incline controls let you adjust your level of incline easily and instantly.</li><li>The maximum user capacity for this Proform treadmill is 300 lbs.<br /></li><li>The Proform 400 CT is sturdy and can stand up to heavy use.</li></ul><br /><a href="http://www.tkqlhce.com/click-3489386-10460334?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.proform.com%2Fwebapp%2Fwcs%2Fstores%2Fservlet%2FProduct_-1_14201_16002_64001_157411&amp;cjsku=PFTL49610" target="_top"><img src="http://www.proform.com/wcsstore/proform/images/catalog/PFTL49610_sml.jpg" alt="Buy the ProForm 400 CT Treadmill now." border="0" /></a><img src="http://www.tqlkg.com/image-3489386-10460334" border="0" height="1" width="1" /><br /><br /><span class="dark-gray">Here is what a Mom of three said about her Proform 400CT. <span style="font-style: italic;">"I bought this treadmill last week and it is  everything I wanted and more. I am a walker and this is perfect for my  workouts. I LOVE the ifit card technology, the Jillian Micheals workout  kicks my butt! Thanks Proform!</span></span><span style="font-style: italic;">"</span><br /><br />*****<br /><br />For reviews of the newest treadmills, check out these sites.<br /><br /><a href="http://www.besttreadmill-reviews.org/">Best Treadmill Reviews</a><br /><a href="http://www.besttreadmill-reviews.org/proform-treadmill-review">Proform Treadmill Reviews</a><div class="blogger-post-footer"><img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/4492444098437691579-7911324563949063993?l=home-exercise-equipment.blogspot.com' alt='' /></div>
