    <item>
      <title>A Review of Chalene Johnson's TurboFire Workouts</title>
      <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/HomeExerciseEquipmentReviewsAndTips/~3/g-0lJ8je2xY/review-of-chalene-johnsons-turbofire.html</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Feb 2012 15:00:39 GMT</pubDate>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div style="text-align: center;"><br /></div><a href="http://teambeachbody.com/shop/-/shopping/TurboFire?referringRepId=38076"><img style="float:left; margin:0 10px 10px 0;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 224px; height: 320px;" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-6y3Gxm0tkNk/TzvgA9HFh2I/AAAAAAAABfQ/EmXpb_hzays/s320/Turbo-Fire.jpg" alt="" id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5709403259631142754" border="0" /></a><br />If you are exercising to burn fat, the <span style="font-weight: bold;">TurboFire Workouts</span> give you the means to charge up your body's metabolism and burn calories much faster. In fact, you could be <span style="font-style: italic;">burning away fat and calories up to nine times as fast.</span><br /><br />The secrets to TurboFire workouts lie in their intensity. Fitness instructor Chalene Johnson makes use of <span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;">High Intensity Interval Training</span> in her upbeat workouts. This method of exercise results in your body burning up to 9 times as much fat and calories.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">As much as 9 times as much fat and calories?</span><br /><br />Yes. Chalene's cardio based workouts combine dance moves, kickboxing drills, and other aerobic moves. During these workout sessions she employs High Intensity Interval Training fire drills. These fire drills are what makes the difference.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">It is different from ordinary cardio.</span> This workout includes one minute high intensity drills that can cause your body to <span style="font-style: italic;">burn calories at an accelerated rate long after you have finished your workout.</span> This accelerated rate of calorie burn can last up to 24 hours. That is why a few minutes of High Intensity Interval Training can be more effective than half an hour or more on a treadmill.<br /><br /><a style="font-weight: bold;" href="http://teambeachbody.com/shop/-/shopping/TurboFire?referringRepId=38076">Learn more or buy TurboFire now directly from Team Beachbody.</a><br /><br /><br />Chalene Johnson, your fitness instructor during the TuboFire Workouts has made these half hour workout session unique. She has custom designed each workout and combined it with choreographed upbeat music to motivate and get the most out of you.<br /><br />With 20 years of fitness experience, Chalene has built a well deserved reputation that has caused people to <span style="font-weight: bold;">wait in line</span> to attend her classes. With TurboFire you'll be able to access this through DVDs in the comfort and privacy of your home.<br /><br />I feel the TurboFire workouts are great for most anyone - but let's take a look at the profiles of those that will likely get the most out of this fitness and weight loss program.<br /><ul><li><span style="font-weight: bold;">First of all, TurboFire is an excellent program for those that want to lose weight and burn fat.</span> The High Intensity Interval Training fire drills, the upbeat motivating music, Chalene's amazing ability to get the most out of you - these all combine to give you the tools you need to see eye popping results.</li><li><span style="font-weight: bold;">People that are training to achieve a lean, fit and toned look will benefit from and enjoy TurboFire.</span> <span style="font-style: italic;">This workout program is not for anyone whose primary objective is to bulk up and add more muscle mass.</span> It <span style="font-style: italic;">is</span> however an excellent program for those that want to build strength and get that tight, fit body.</li><li><span style="font-weight: bold;">If you have been through one of Chalene Johnson's other workout programs</span> and are looking for her 'next generation' workouts, TurboFire is for you. You already know the energy and motivating Chalene brings. You're just looking for more!</li><li><span style="font-weight: bold;">Folks that are not seeing results with their cardio program might want to migrate over to TurboFire.</span> Has your current program gone flat? Are you not making the gains you were previously? TurboFire may just be the solution! With it's High Intensity Interval Training, this fitness program can give you the push to help you start losing those pounds again.</li><li><span style="font-weight: bold;">Men and women that want or need to gradually get into shape can benefit from Turbo Fire.</span> You can learn the routines at your own pace and use a special schedule to get prepared for those high intensity fire drills.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><a style="font-weight: bold;" href="http://teambeachbody.com/shop/-/shopping/TurboFire?referringRepId=38076">Get further details or buy TurboFire now at Beachbody.</a></p><p><br /></p><p><span style="font-weight: bold;">What are the men and women that have purchased TurboFire saying?</span></p><p>The TurboFire workout received <span style="font-style: italic;">4.3 stars out of a possible 5 stars</span> from the 129 customer reviews we found at the Amazon customer review page for this product. You can access all the reviews <a target="_blank" href="http://www.amazon.com/review/B003TQITGO/?_encoding=UTF8&amp;showViewpoints=1&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957">here.</a><img src="https://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=folthenewyory-20&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=1" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;" border="0" height="1" width="1" /></p><p>Reading through these reviewers we found a wealth of useful, unbiased information. Most of the women and men liked Chalene's instruction style but some cautioned it takes a little bit of time to get used to her 'get in and go' style. </p><p>The prep schedule was praised as helpful for anyone that needs to ramp up to the intensity of these workouts.  We found more than one review stating that these workout are intense. Here is how one put it.<br /></p><p><span style="font-style: italic;"></span><span style="font-style: italic;"></span></p><blockquote><span style="font-style: italic;">" ... I have done TurboJam (Chalene Johnson's other major cardio DVD program)  since 2006 and have enjoyed it immensely.  TurboFire is billed as a more  intense, complex cousin to TurboJam, and I have to agree with that.   Even with over four years of pretty difficult cardio conditioning,  TurboFire was still a challenge from the outset.  Even the 30-minute  Fire workout is more difficult than any TurboJam program...."</span> Rachel from customer reviews.</blockquote><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">TurboFire Results</span><br /><br /><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-YOa7KdnZ4D8/T0JWkkgT3VI/AAAAAAAABf0/xFKZHt3UGHw/s1600/turbo%2Bfire%2Bresults.jpg"><img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 400px; height: 121px;" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-YOa7KdnZ4D8/T0JWkkgT3VI/AAAAAAAABf0/xFKZHt3UGHw/s400/turbo%2Bfire%2Bresults.jpg" alt="" id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5711222463733685586" border="0" /></a>Getting results with the TurboFire workouts is what it is all about, right? Well, the weight and fat losses we've found have been impressive. Of course, your mileage may vary. The folks that got results followed the program including eating properly.<br /><br />In the video below, Ashley talks about how she transformed herself with TurboFire. She lost 40 lbs. in the 1st 5 months. She lost 43.5 inches and she says she never felt better. <span style="font-style: italic;">Way to go, Ashley!</span><br /><br /><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/vfyVzlpp8Nk?rel=0" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" width="400"></iframe><br /><br />After 90 days, Liz needs some new skinny jeans!<br /><br /><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/oCar0VWyoM8?rel=0" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" width="400"></iframe><br /><br />Stacy is the mom of two boys, is almost 40 - and now has the body she had never had before.<br /><br /><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/HPCCcnSC6O0?rel=0" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" width="400"></iframe><br /><br />With High Intensity Interval Training, the motivation of Chalene Johnson and fun challenging workouts, TurboFire can be your path to transforming your body to what you have always hoped it would be.<br /><br /><a style="font-weight: bold;" href="http://teambeachbody.com/shop/-/shopping/TurboFire?referringRepId=38076">Buy TurboFire now direct from Beachbody.</a><br /><br />Are you willing to <span style="font-weight: bold;">commit to TurboFire</span> and get turbocharged fitness results?<br /><br /><div style="text-align: center;"> *****</div><br /><br />See also:<br /><a href="http://www.squidoo.com/turbo-fire-workout_with-chalene-johnson">TurboFire Workout with Chalene Johnson</a><div class="blogger-post-footer"><img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/4492444098437691579-8154654477207151804?l=home-exercise-equipment.blogspot.com' alt='' /></div>
<p><a href="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/vc_rAsFkU0H9Maze03U_TP-F14g/0/da"><img src="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/vc_rAsFkU0H9Maze03U_TP-F14g/0/di" border="0" ismap="true"></img></a><br/>
<a href="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/vc_rAsFkU0H9Maze03U_TP-F14g/1/da"><img src="http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/vc_rAsFkU0H9Maze03U_TP-F14g/1/di" border="0" ismap="true"></img></a></p><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/HomeExerciseEquipmentReviewsAndTips/~4/g-0lJ8je2xY" height="1" width="1"/>]]></content:encoded>
      <enclosure url="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/home-exercise-equipment-reviews-and-tips/Home_Exercise_Equipment_Reviews_And_Tips-A_Review_of_Chalene_Johnsons_TurboFire_Workouts.mp3" length="2918103" type="audio/mpeg" />
