      <title>Horizon Fitness T101-3 Treadmill (2012 Model)</title>
      <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/HomeExerciseEquipmentReviewsAndTips/~3/OEF66zg8-fk/horizon-fitness-t101-3-treadmill-2012.html</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Jan 2012 19:40:19 GMT</pubDate>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B005AC1H6Y/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B005AC1H6Y"><img style="float:left; margin:0 10px 10px 0;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 300px; height: 300px;" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-BetV2P3Opb0/Tx7XH20ejiI/AAAAAAAABco/JuJKJ86ZMOY/s400/Horizon%2BFitness%2BT101-3%2BTreadmill%2B%25282012%2BModel%2529.jpg" alt="" id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5701230708272303650" border="0" /></a><br />The <span style="font-weight: bold;">Horizon Fitness T101-3 Treadmill (2012 Model)</span> is an economical home treadmill that's received high marks from men and women that have purchased this treadmill and use it in their homes.<br /><br />Whenever you buy a piece of home exercise equipment online, you want to know for sure that you are getting a quality, worry free product.<br /><br />Spending hundreds of dollars on a home treadmill that you've only seen via your web browser requires a certain amount of faith in the company from which you are purchasing a machine you expect to have in your house for years.<br /><br />Of the <span style="font-weight: bold;">over one dozen customer reviews</span> already submitted at Amazon, the Horizon Fitness T101-3 Treadmill (2012 Model) has received a cumulative grade of 4.3 out of a possible 5 stars. That is a very good rating but not everyone was happy. You can read all the reviews and learn more at the following link.<br /><br /><a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B005AC1H6Y/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B005AC1H6Y">Find out more about the Horizon Fitness T101-3 Treadmill (2012 Model)</a><img src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=folthenewyory-20&amp;l=as2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B005AC1H6Y" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;" width="1" border="0" height="1" /><br /><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">Features and specs of the  2012 model of the Horizon Fitness T101-3 Treadmill </span><br /><ul><li>Let's start with the power plant. The T101-3 has a 2.25 horsepower continuous duty motor that <span style="font-weight: bold;">operates powerfully and quietly</span>. </li><li>The frame is large and sturdy. It will stand up to heavy duty workout sessions and has a 300 lb. maximum user capacity. One thing to consider: This is a pretty heavy treadmill ( the shipping weight is 180 lbs.) . You'll want to take this into consideration if you'll need help in getting it into place when your treadmill arrives.</li><li>One of my favorite features of this treadmill is the deck on which you do your walking, jogging, and running. This PerfectFLEX deck has <span style="font-weight: bold;">cushioning</span> that provides you with the correct amount of support and shock absorption. </li><li>The running belt surface  is 20 inches wide and 55 inches long. It is durable and the belt is 1.4 centimeters thick and made of a two ply material. </li><li>You'll be able to <span style="font-weight: bold;">choose from 9 workout program options</span>. Pick your choice of a workout target of either a time, a distance, or a number of calories burned. Then combine that with your choice of either a manual workout, interval training, or a workout for weight loss. The workout that results will be tailored uniquely to your workout demands.</li><li>The Horizon T-101 is a fold-able treadmill. This lets you free up space when you're not using it. The FeatherLIGHT lift make <span style="font-weight: bold;">raising and lowering the running deck very easy</span>. It has two hydraulic lifts to assist you to move the deck up or lower it.</li><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/--AYVpMjiILE/Tx7rnnZR4PI/AAAAAAAABdA/fx-mFjS9gaU/s1600/Horizon%2BFitness%2BT101-3%2Bcomputer%2Bconsole.jpg"><img style="float:right; margin:0 0 10px 10px;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 200px; height: 200px;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/--AYVpMjiILE/Tx7rnnZR4PI/AAAAAAAABdA/fx-mFjS9gaU/s200/Horizon%2BFitness%2BT101-3%2Bcomputer%2Bconsole.jpg" alt="" id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5701253244120064242" border="0" /></a><li>The computer console lets you track your workout progress from 3 orange LED windows, an LED brickyard display, and through target/workout indicators.</li><li><span style="font-weight: bold;">Sonic Surround speakers</span> with MP3 input let you play music through the console speakers to enhance your workout experience.</li><li>The<span style="font-weight: bold;"> Coolfit fitness fan </span>that's built into the T-101-3 treadmill gives you a little air to make workouts more comfortable.</li><li>The speed range goes <span style="font-weight: bold;">up to 10 miles per hour</span> and you can adjust your level of incline from level up to as much as 10 degrees.</li><li>Treadmill Doctor selected this treadmill as a <span style="font-style: italic;">"Best Buy"</span> in it's category. By now you can see why.</li></ul><p>We found the best deal for the Horizon Fitness T-101-3 ( 2012 model) - and many other home treadmills - at Amazon.com . Prices change frequently so to find out the latest price and how much you can save, click the following link. <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B005AC1H6Y/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B005AC1H6Y">Learn more or buy now at Amazon.</a></p><p><span style="font-weight: bold;">More on what T-101 purchasers had to say.</span></p><p>The men and women that have already purchased this home treadmill were by and large casual or recreational exercisers. A few self described "gym rats" also selected the Horizon Fitness T-101 treadmill.</p><p>They felt this treadmill was <span style="font-weight: bold;">good for losing weight and heart rate training</span>. Low impact aerobic training, performance training, and distance/endurance training were all types of exercise training for which this treadmill was used.</p><p>Items customers selected as positive of the Horizon T-101 included quiet operation, sturdy design, and ease of storage. The ease or difficulty of initially setting up this treadmill garnered mixed reviews.</p><p>Here is an excerpt for one "Very happy" review.</p><p><span style="font-style: italic;"></span></p><blockquote><span style="font-style: italic;">" ... I went through multiple review forums looking for a treadmill under $700  and finally settled on this. I'm really happy with my choice. You  basically get all you need from this treadmill. I don't notice any  difference from the one sitting in the gym regarding performance. I ran  on the treadmill for a few times at 6.5. It was doing great. ..." <a target="_blank" href="http://www.amazon.com/review/B005AC1H6Y/?_encoding=UTF8&amp;showViewpoints=1&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957">( read more here )</a><img src="https://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=folthenewyory-20&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=1" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;" width="1" border="0" height="1" /></span></blockquote><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">What we think. </span>If you are someone that uses a treadmill for 20 or 30 minutes at a time - several times a week, we feel like this compact home treadmill could be a good match for you. Since it is a Horizon Fitness treadmill, it comes from good ( award winning ) stock.<br /><br />It is a sturdy, well made treadmill - but not the biggest they make. If you are a serious runner or want a treadmill you can use to train for competition we suggest the <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B003TNNPZC/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B003TNNPZC">Horizon Fitness T202 Treadmill</a><img src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=folthenewyory-20&amp;l=as2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B003TNNPZC" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;" width="1" border="0" height="1" /> - or better yet the <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B003Z4AAPI/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=folthenewyory-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B003Z4AAPI">Sole F80 Treadmill (2011 Model)</a><img src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=folthenewyory-20&amp;l=as2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B003Z4AAPI" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;" width="1" border="0" height="1" />.<br /><br />But if you're looking for something that's reasonably priced and with several performance features like the cushioned deck and variety of workout programs, the Horizon Fitness T101-3 Treadmill (2012 Model) makes a good choice.<br /><br /><div style="text-align: center;">******<br /></div><br />For more on good quality home treadmills be sure to check out:<br /><br /><a href="http://www.besttreadmill-reviews.org/">Best Treadmill Reviews</a><div class="blogger-post-footer"><img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/4492444098437691579-4322911851160805811?l=home-exercise-equipment.blogspot.com' alt='' /></div>
